==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Frost-free
<hw>Frost"-free</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>not accumulating frost; -- used
especially of refrigerators with an automatic defrost cycle such that
the freezer compartment remains free of ice without need for a manual
defrosting.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Frost signal</ent>⟦br⟧
